          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Depreciation Fairness Act of 2015 </strong></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to make permanent the 15-year recovery period for qualified leasehold improvement property, qualified restaurant property, and qualified retail improvement property for purposes of the tax deduction for depreciation. </p>]]></text>
